prod.full_name: Jordan 1 Retro Low White Ghost Green Black
prod.path: Home/Sneakers/Air Jordan/1/Low/Jordan 1 Retro Low White Ghost Green Black
prod.desciption:
The Air Jordan 1 Low White Ghost Green features a white leather upper with Ghost Green overlays and Swooshes. From there, a checker-board woven Nike tag is stitched atop the tongue. An embroidered mini Swoosh on the toe wrap and silver heel tab adds the finishing touches to this OG model.

The Air Jordan 1 Low White Ghost Green released in May of 2021 and retailed for $130.
